Its Easy to do in pascal as well as C++ using the PORT[address] command.
Ive used It before to control external devices.
A normal parralell pot has 8 outputs D0 - 7 and a few lines that you can use
as inputs (not sure which ones though?)

The port voltage is 5V so you may need some buffering...

